column1: If toothed equal to no AND ( region equal to arctic OR head equal to no ) , then fendle.
If arms equal to no OR ( head equal to yes AND region equal to atlantic ) , then not zav.
If arms equal to yes AND ( toothed equal to yes OR fins equal to yes ) , then not tulver.
If head equal to yes AND ( region equal to atlantic OR arms equal to yes ) , then not pimwit.
